PXID F1 Electric Scooter – Neon Night Lights
Specifications:
Brand: PXID F1 Tire Size: 10-inch tubeless tires Max Speed: Up to 49 km/h Range: 40 km (on a full charge) Max Load: 150 kg Lights: LED spotlight Weight: 27.5 kg Color: Neon Night Lights Max Climb Angle: Up to 35° Material: Aluminum alloy body Motor Type: Front-wheel drive (FWD) Brakes: Drum brake (front) + electric brake (rear) Motor Power: 500W Charging Time: 3–5 hours Voltage: 48V Charger: 110V–240V, 50Hz–60Hz Battery: 13Ah lithium battery Suspension: Dual (front and back) App Function: Not supported Water Resistance: IP54

The PXID F1 Electric Scooter combines speed, durability, and modern design. With its powerful 500W motor, dual suspension, and tubeless tires, this scooter is perfect for urban commutes or adventurous rides. Explore in style with its eye-catching Neon Night Lights!
